# ===================================================================
# Magma Engine - .gitignore
# 涵盖环境：Visual Studio, CMake, Qt, Windows
# ===================================================================

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. 编译输出与 CMake 缓存目录 (最占空间的大头)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
/out/
/build/
/bin/
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CMakeScripts/
Makefile
cmake_install.cmake
install_manifest.txt
compile_commands.json
CTestTestfile.cmake
_deps/

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. Visual Studio 本地工作区与缓存 (截图里的红框部分)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.suo
*.db
*.opendb
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.sqlite3
*.log

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. Qt 自动生成的中间文件
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*_autogen/
moc_*.cpp
moc_*.h
qrc_*.cpp
ui_*.h
*.qm

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. 二进制产物与中间编译文件
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.exe
*.dll
*.lib
*.obj
*.o
*.a
*.ilk
*.pdb
*.idb
*.exp
*.ilk
*.pch

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. 操作系统产生的垃圾文件
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. 特殊放行规则 (反向过滤)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# 如果你希望某些特定的空文件夹被 Git 追踪，可以在里面放一个 .gitkeep 文件
# !.gitkeep